## Q: How to disable annotation rotation?

If you wish to disable annotation rotation UI, call [`disableAnnotationRotation()`][] in [`PdfActivityConfiguration.Builder`][] or [`PdfConfiguration.Builder`][]:

```kotlin
val configuration = PdfActivityConfiguration.Builder(context)
    .disableAnnotationRotation()
    .build()

// You can set the configuration when building PdfActivity Intent.
val intent = PdfActivityIntentBuilder.fromUri(context, documentUri)
    .configuration(configuration)
    .build()

context.startActivity(intent)
```

[`disableannotationrotation()`]: https://pspdfkit.com/api/android/reference/com/pspdfkit/configuration/activity/PdfActivityConfiguration.Builder.html#disableAnnotationRotation()